features: ⚡FASTER & MORE STABLE: The 10 inch tablet equipped with the newest Android 12 is more customizable and personalized for you and has a heavier focus on performance and privacy than Android 11. Equipped MT8183 chipset using a low-power 12nm process, combines an octa-core CPU with 4 Arm Cortex-A73 ‘big’ cores and 4 Cortex-A53 cores all operating up to 2GHz. The powerful Arm Mali-G72-class graphics processor operating up to 800MHz makes it run smoothly even as a gaming tablet.

🔋7000mAh BATTERY & LARGE MEMORY: The Android 12 Tablet equipped with a 7000mAh large capacity battery achieves up to 10 hours for playing games, 12 hours for videos, and about 14 hours for reading or browsing. Comes with 4GB+64GB built-in storage and up to 512GB expandable storage (TF Card). More apps, songs, videos, and photos can be easily saved on your tablet. Tituta android tablets have passed the GMS certification. You have full access to the latest Google service.

💎G+G SENSITIVE TOUCHSCREEN: Made of surface tempered glass+glass GLASS material production screen with the characteristics of support hard wear, corrosion resistance, high light transmittance, control feel smooth and high reliability. Not easy to leave scratches. A 10-point multi-touch screen allows you to easily zoom, flick, rotate, drag, pinch or use other gestures with up to ten fingers on the screen at the same time.

📷HD DISPLAY & 5+8M PIXEL LENS: The 10 in tablet equipped with high resolution of 1280*800 IPS display, comfortable 16:10 large screen adapted to YouTube, TikTok, Netflix, Disney Plus, allowing you to enjoy your leasure time with a comfortable video viewing experience. Equipped 8MP rear camera with auto focus and flash, shooting is equally clear during the day and night. The 5MP front camera bring excellent clarity during video calls.

📌MUTI-FUNCTION: Our tabletas support split-screen and wireless projection. The split screen function allows two apps to work together on the same screen, making your work more efficient. Wireless projection allows you to connect to larger screen devices, and achieve a realistic viewing experience.

reviews.reviewText: Great tablet. Good price. Wonderful display. Fast delivery and fast is.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 14, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is a nice little tablet for the price. So far I've had no problem with it and it always connects easily to the internet. Has a pretty nice picture and well worth the money.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Decent but crashes
reviews.reviewText: This tablet I bought for my 3 year old to play her educational games on, so I didn’t need much. It is fast, bright and simple to use. That being said, it does have moments when you turn it on and the screen goes black and displays foreign letters. In my experience i can reset it no problem by inserting a small pin into the tiny reset hole on the side. Frustrating, but for the price it still serves its purpose for my needs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Died in less than 4 months
reviews.reviewText: I purchased a Tibuta 10” E200 Tablet on Aug23, 2023. The unit died on Dec 7, less than 4months from purchase. This tablet was purchased primarily as a e-reader with a little bit of web browsing. The unit rarely left my study. I tried the usual corrective steps to bring the tablet back to life – charged with new charger, pressed reset. Nothing worked. As directed by Amazon, I contacted both the seller and manufacturer via email. It has been 5 days since my request for help – no reply. Poor quality and terrible customer service.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
Reviewed in the United States on September 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I am loving this!
reviews.reviewText: Besides a great price, and fast shipping, I am loving Tibuta 10 inch. The screen is nice and large and the picture is large enough for people with sight issues. Nice and bright on 80% night mode.What I really love is that the power cord plug hole and the earphone plug hole are both on top of the tablet instead of the bottom when you have the screen rotation set to tall instead of wide. I never could understand why phones and tablets have them on the bottom!The only con is that my stylus doesn't work that well with this screen - I have to tap pretty hard - but the touch sensitivity is perfect for the old fashioned finger.I might have to get one for the hubs...

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars No name, Gr8 tablet!
reviews.reviewText: After carefully studying the specifications I decided to give this tablet a try. It's fast, crystal clear, with good speakers. It works just like my Samsung tablet for a lot less money. Very satisfied!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great 10" Tablet for the Money
reviews.reviewText: Like the Tablet. Easy to use. A bit Heavy as others state. However, I like the Metal case. Responds well for my purposes. Quality Sound & Pocture is more than expected: glad as I am a Senior was comcerned about both.Unless you're a Hardcore techy...I think you'd like this. I gave it 4 Stars because I haven't had the opportunity to fully experience all that this Tablet offers.
